  "prompt": "How is the academics in Hindu Rao Medical College?",
  "response": "Hindu Rao Medical College, located in Delhi, India, is affiliated with the Delhi University and is known for its medical education and training programs. The college offers undergraduate (MBBS) and postgraduate courses in various medical specialties. \n\nAcademically, Hindu Rao Medical College is recognized for its rigorous curriculum, which includes theoretical learning as well as practical and clinical exposure. The college has a dedicated faculty that provides instruction and mentorship to students. The academic environment encourages research and participation in various medical conferences and workshops.\n\nThe college also has associated hospitals where students can gain hands-on experience with patients, which is crucial for developing clinical skills. Overall, the academic experience at Hindu Rao Medical College aims to prepare students to become competent and compassionate healthcare professionals.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, including admission details, course offerings, and student experiences, it is advisable to check the official college website or contact current students or alumni.",
